ESDA *is a *Software Development* firm with a mission of providing innovative services and vision of serving clients across the globe. It is a customer centric Information Technology Company which specializes in Business Application Development. ESDA’s offerings are highly customizable and scalable. It also provide Web Development services and believes in providing 360 degree support to its clients.
ESDA provides Web Development services like Web designing, App Development, Digital Marketing, Graphic Designing, Hosting, Time and Material and Gap Analysis Consultancy apart from these service, it is also working towards launching applications/software for the online market as its products.
We are actively looking for Flutter Developers with 1 to 3 years of experience in developing Mobile Applications using Hybrid Technologies (Ionic, Flutter, React js). *
Required skills: *
Should have experience in working with two or more iOS/Android apps developed with Flutter. Either deployed on the App Store/Google Play or available on Github;
1 to 3 years in mobile software development;
Experience with third-party libraries and APIs;
Understanding of the Agile development life-cycle;
Experience with automated testing and building;
Experience with Git, Jenkins, or other version control tools;
Ability to write readable code, create extensive documentation for existing code, and refactor the previously written code into readable state.
Job Type: Full-time

Salary: ₹25,000.00 - ₹30,000.00 per month

